description: GX-D1081 Switch is embedded with Green Network Technology which allows users to conserve energy and still enjoy a lag free network. The VIP port or top priority port contains the highest priority queue occupancy that ensures 80% data is transferred to there first. Asus GX-D1081 Gigabit switch is the best high-speed, power-saving solution for home / SOHO networking.
title: ASUS 8-Port Gigabit Green Switch and VIP Port (GX-D1081/V2)
